g.text: UML Diagram: Class Key in Context
- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.
- Click on a name to go to the corresponding page.

a.title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.
a.xlink:title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.

a.title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.

a.title: ― DataSet: Organized collection of data based on keys.
a.xlink:title: ― DataSet: Organized collection of data based on keys.

a.title: ― Universe: Specialized unit type, with the specialization based upon characteristics other than time and geography.
a.xlink:title: ― Universe: Specialized unit type, with the specialization based upon characteristics other than time and geography.

a.title: ― Unit: Individual object of interest for some statistical activity, such as data collection.
a.xlink:title: ― Unit: Individual object of interest for some statistical activity, such as data collection.

a.title: ― KeyDefinition: Collection of concepts that uniquely defines a collection of data points in a dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyDefinition: Collection of concepts that uniquely defines a collection of data points in a dataset.

a.title: ― Key: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― Key: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dataset.

a.title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.

a.title: ― LongKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a long dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― LongKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a long dataset.

a.title: ― DimensionalKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dimensional dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionalKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dimensional dataset.

a.title: ― WideKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a wide dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― WideKey: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a wide dataset.
